economic crisis.

00:14:53.580 --> 00:14:57.020
So we've developed some pretty
interesting R and D. You guys

00:14:57.020 --> 00:14:58.245
clearly have there.

00:14:58.245 --> 00:15:02.140
But there just aren't that
many efforts like that.

00:15:02.140 --> 00:15:05.500
You see the big software
players, Microsoft coming out

00:15:05.500 --> 00:15:12.950
with hardware, Amazon, Android,
Facebook entering

00:15:12.950 --> 00:15:14.570
because they're frustrated.

00:15:14.570 --> 00:15:17.050
They can't just continue to let
Apple eat their breakfast,

00:15:17.050 --> 00:15:19.290
lunch, and dinner.

00:15:19.290 --> 00:15:24.510
Dell, HP, Nokia they all
misstepped or Apple executed

00:15:24.510 --> 00:15:26.980
well, but it doesn't matter.

00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:28.630
You see people filling
in for that.

00:15:28.630 --> 00:15:34.120
But it's been walking
through the

00:15:34.120 --> 00:15:36.290
valley of death or something.

00:15:36.290 --> 00:15:40.461
It feels a lot like that through
this period of time.

