There's something like
1,200 people working

00:16:19.170 --> 00:16:21.890
on different things.

00:16:21.890 --> 00:16:24.480
And there's a lot of rumors that
they're coming out with

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:26.000
other sets of devices.

