So it's just like a lot of
continuous innovation.

00:17:04.730 --> 00:17:07.690
I mean, for us, like Chrome, we
have Chromebooks and so on,

00:17:07.690 --> 00:17:12.339
just like filling a market where
people, in addition to

00:17:12.339 --> 00:17:13.430
meeting the [? tablets, ?]

