be a little TV, right?

00:29:19.740 --> 00:29:20.930
We need screens.

00:29:20.930 --> 00:29:23.920
The world's information is
digital, the way we access

00:29:23.920 --> 00:29:26.420
that information is through
the screen.

00:29:26.420 --> 00:29:29.600
And that's why I'm quite
fascinated by the work that

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:31.250
you're doing.

00:29:31.250 --> 00:29:33.790
What can that be?

00:29:33.790 --> 00:29:38.760
